  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on UNESCO World Heritage Sites",
  "purpose": "The APPG seeks to grow support and recognition for British World Heritage Sites (WHS) and the grassroots organisations managing them; develop WHS as assets for soft power by sharing good practice internationally; articulate the significance and benefits of WHS, particularly lesser-known ones domestically and globally, in achieving balanced economic growth.",
